              {
                "node": {
                  "text": "Layered with old car magazines, vintage advertising and custom screen prints, each of @duffyleg’s creations carries a history that is uniquely American. He loves the process as much as he does the final piece. Using his #Surface to design, plan and process his work—he’s telling America’s car culture history in larger-than-life hot rod form. See more of Duffy’s work by clicking the link in our bio."
                }
              }
            ]
