              {
                "node": {
                  "text": "With 15 World Championship podiums in his career, Flavio Canto achieved greatness in Judo. Using the same education and discipline he learned through sport, he’s now mentoring youth in Rio de Janeiro at his Reação Institute. Through his work he’s helped train new Olympians, while also fostering them in education and professional development. Learn more about his cause and how you can help on Coletivo do Esporte, a crowdfunding site dedicated to helping Brazilian youth and communities."
                }
              }
            ]
