            "edges": [
              {
                "node": {
                  "text": "From the hot rod shop to the snowboard industry to the art gallery, @duffyleg’s road to art reflects his personal style. Duffy uses his @Surface to create layered stories that connect two unlikely audiences: car buffs and art connoisseurs. With graffiti-style cars plastered around the country, and a new art exhibition hitting Seattle next spring, he’s creating discoverable moments, for car enthusiasts and art fans alike. “If it makes them laugh, cool. If you take a photo of it, even better. If they talk about it and it makes them interested in art, double win. It's really about the interaction.” Want to see if it moves you? Click the link in our bio."
                }
              }
            ]
